    <content type="html">&lt;section class=&quot;hero&quot;&gt;&lt;h1&gt;Upper Caboolture&lt;/h1&gt;&lt;/section&gt;&lt;section class=&quot;content&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Our studio is in Upper Caboolture, Queensland, Australia. Lots of sunshine and warm weather. &lt;a href=&quot;/currawong/&quot;&gt;Currawongs&lt;/a&gt; are plentiful, as are many other birds. It&#39;s a lovely place and we hope to show you more in our &lt;a href=&quot;/projects/&quot;&gt;games&lt;/a&gt;!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/section&gt;</content>
